---
import Layout from '@components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - How's Pot Doing?">
  <article class="about">
    <h1>How the Legality of cannabis is calculated</h1>

    <p>Each state gets a <strong>0-100%</strong> legality score based on cannabis access.</p>

    <div class="scoring">
      <div class="score-item rec">
        <span class="points">80%</span>
        <span class="label">Recreational legal</span>
      </div>
      <div class="score-item bonus">
        <span class="points">+10%</span>
        <span class="label">Can buy in stores</span>
      </div>
      <div class="score-item bonus">
        <span class="points">+10%</span>
        <span class="label">Can grow at home</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="divider">— or if recreational isn't legal —</p>

    <div class="scoring med-only">
      <div class="score-item med">
        <span class="points">30%</span>
        <span class="label">Medical only</span>
      </div>
      <div class="score-item bonus">
        <span class="points">+10%</span>
        <span class="label">Patients can buy</span>
      </div>
      <div class="score-item bonus">
        <span class="points">+10%</span>
        <span class="label">Patients can grow</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="note">
      <strong>100%</strong> = full recreational access<br />
      <strong>50%</strong> = best medical-only<br />
      <strong>0%</strong> = fully illegal
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-wrap-style: balance;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .scoring {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .score-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .points {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    min-width: 50px;
  }

  .label {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .rec {
    background: #d4edda;
  }

  .rec .points {
    color: #00bf00;
  }

  .med {
    background: #e6e6f3;
  }

  .med .points {
    color: #6666ff;
  }

  .bonus {
    background: #f5f5f5;
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }

  .divider {
    color: #888;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin: 1.25rem 0;
  }

  .note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .back-link {
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .back-link a {
    color: #00bf00;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
